News.headline: FA Youth Cup: Dagenham and Redbridge v Colchester United
News.page_title: FA Youth Cup: Dagenham and Redbridge v Colchester United
News.URL_keywords: FA Youth Cup: Dagenham and Redbridge v Colchester United
News.short_description: The Daggers Academy are playing at home to Colchester United tonight in the first round of the FA Youth Cup.
News.description:
The game will be played at the Chigwell Construction Stadium Wednesday 2nd November, 7pm kick off.

Come down and support our Academy with ticket prices starting at just £1! 

Ticket prices:
Adults: £4.00 
Concessions/Juniors: £1.00
